        <pre><code class="highlight"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">CharlesOliverNutter</span> <span class="no">&lt; Human</span>
  <span class="c"># Architect &amp; Technologist</span></code></pre>
        <p>
          Three decades of software development, deep expertise in JVM internals, Ruby, bytecode, and invokedynamic. Co-lead of JRuby since 2004. Regular conference speaker on Java, Ruby, and the weird wonderful space where they overlap.
        </p>
