          Charlie has released commercial software, managed open-source projects, led enterprise applications, and contributed hundreds of thousands of lines of code globally. His talks on JVM bytecode, invokedynamic, and JIT compilers are consistently among the most popular at Java and Ruby conferences worldwide.
        </p>
